'''eMonkeyz''' is a Professional Esports Club founded on November, 2015. Their motto is "He have come to stay. Feel the power. Feel the wildness. We are eMonkeyz!". They were partnered with Spanish football club [[wikipedia:SD Huesca|SD Huesca]] during most part of the 2022 season.

== History ==
'''eMonkeyz''' was born in November 2015 from the merger of [[Celerius e-Sports]], club with a long history on the national scene, and '''Bananized''', a group of professionals with extensive experience in the esports sector.

